JsonSchema.Label: Azure Subscription Cost Categories
JsonSchema.Hint:
The Cost Categories the subscriptions managed by services in this organization are billed to when the subscriptions are not marked as Hosted-On-Behalf-Of (HOBO).
Default: COGS for Prod subscriptions and R&D/OPEX for NonProd subscriptions.
Aggregation: values lower in the tree take precedence over higher ones.

Properties.Label: Production
Properties.Hint: The AIRS cost category of Production subscriptions (ex: FX for COGS, FR for OPEX/R&D). Default: FX.
Properties.Name: Production

Properties.Label: NonProd
Properties.Hint: The AIRS cost category of Non-Production subscriptions (ex: FX for COGS, FR for OPEX/R&D). Default: FR.
Properties.Name: NonProd

Properties.Name: Aliases
Properties.RegexErrorMessage: The Finance Manager field must contain a semicolon-separated list of lower-case user aliases without spaces (ex: 'jasonz;bharry').

Properties.Label: Node Description and Code
Properties.Hint: The description and code of the node.
Properties.Name: NodeDescAndCode
Properties.RegexErrorMessage: The Function description and code must be of the form 'Azure CloudES (HM1F)'.
Properties.SourceKustoQuery: cluster('datastudiostreaming.kusto.windows.net').database('SharedSlow').AIRS_ProfitCenterOrgHierarchy_Snapshot | extend ItemKey = iff(ExecOrgDescAndCode contains "term", ExecOrgDescAndCode,iff(ExecOrgSummaryDescAndCode contains "term",ExecOrgSummaryDescAndCode,iff(OrgDetailDescAndCode contains "term",OrgDetailDescAndCode,iff(FuncSummaryDescAndCode contains "term",FuncSummaryDescAndCode,iff(FuncDescAndCode contains "term",FuncDescAndCode,iff(FuncDetailDescAndCode contains "term",FuncDetailDescAndCode,"")))))) | where ItemKey != "" | distinct  ItemKey | project ItemKey, ItemValue = ItemKey

JsonSchema.Label: Azure Subscription Profit Centers
JsonSchema.Hint:
The Profit Center Codes (PCCodes) the subscriptions managed by services in this organization are billed to when the subscriptions are not marked as Hosted-On-Behalf-Of (HOBO).
Aggregation: values lower in the tree get appended to higher ones.

Properties.Label: PCCode
Properties.Hint: Profit Center Code (PCCode)
Properties.Name: PCCode
Properties.RegexErrorMessage: The PCCode must be a capital P followed by 5 or 8 digits (ex: P10041368)
Properties.SourceKustoQuery: cluster('datastudiostreaming.kusto.windows.net').database('SharedSlow').AIRS_GL04ProfitCenter_Snapshot | where ProfitCenterCode contains 'term' and ProfitCenterActiveInd == 'Y' | extend FuncCode = iif(SECFunctionalAreaCode=="FG", "G&A", iif(SECFunctionalAreaCode=="FX", "COGS", iif(SECFunctionalAreaCode=="FR", "R&D", "S&M"))) | project ItemKey = ProfitCenterCode, ItemValue = strcat(ProfitCenterCode," (",FuncCode,")"," : ", ProfitCenterLongDesc) | take 5
